  <summary date="2004-09-08T16:37:18Z" status="Introduced in House">Agricultural Assistance Act of 2004 - Directs the Secretary of Agriculture to provide: (1) emergency financial assistance to agricultural producers who have incurred qualifying 2004 crop losses due to weather or related conditions; and (2) payments to livestock producers who have incurred 2004 losses in an emergency- or disaster-designated county.

Sets forth crop payment rate and eligibility provisions.</summary>
